{"tid":1150290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扶手變床位！學童港鐵展神功 網民狂贈四字真言","createTime":"2019-05-11T17:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T17:32:19.000Z","uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03eb42a4b655856562f0a1592ce02432c692b05e","tid":1150290,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T17:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mua1Fjh_s5OabMA7tJcEXQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/f0f300bcc3b30c5ff51d180fdb588b7a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fmua1Fjh_s5OabMA7tJcEXQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Ff0f300bcc3b30c5ff51d180fdb588b7a&h=0634aadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高手在民間！近日港鐵有小學生「離晒地」，表演橫躺扶手，引來網民驚嘆︰「古墓傳人」。<br />\n<br />\n有網民周五（10日）在Facebook群組「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」發起寫作大考驗，讓網民以四個字為題形容一位奇人異士。從其照片所見，有穿校服的學童「身懷絕技」，在車廂內使出一招「反地心吸力」，整個身體橫躺在扶手與車廂牆壁之間。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民嘖嘖稱奇，紛紛響應題目，以四字戲言：「體操王子」、「國家棟樑」、「技驚四座」、「我欣賞你」、「老竇唔理」、「讀乜學校」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%89%B6%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%8A%E5%BA%8A%E4%BD%8D%EF%BC%81%E5%AD%B8%E7%AB%A5%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%B1%95%E7%A5%9E%E5%8A%9F%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%8B%82%E8%B4%88%E5%9B%9B%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%9F%E8%A8%80-070834477.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%2589%25B6%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E5%25BA%258A%25E4%25BD%258D%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25B1%2595%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%258A%259F%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%258B%2582%25E8%25B4%2588%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25A8%2580-070834477.html&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNW34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=d8aacee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%89%B6%E6%89%8B%E8%AE%8A%